  "remarks": "Limited Liability Company “Commercial Vehicles – GAZ Group” is Russia’s top producer of commercial vehicles. The company’s product portfolio includes light and medium-duty commercial vehicles, buses, engines and over 500 types of special vehicles. Limited Liability Company “Commercial Vehicles – GAZ Group” provides “GAZ” manufactured vehicles to the Russian Armed Forces, which are used in the war of aggression against Ukraine.",
